-spec count(Num1 :: unicode:unicode_binary(), Num2 :: unicode:unicode_binary(), Min_sum :: integer(), Max_sum :: integer()) -> integer().
count(Num1, Num2, Min_sum, Max_sum) ->
    N1 = binary_to_integer(Num1),
    N2 = binary_to_integer(Num2),
    count_good_ints(N1, N2, Min_sum, Max_sum, 0).

count_good_ints(N1, N2, Min_sum, Max_sum, Acc) when N1 > N2 ->
    Acc;
count_good_ints(N, N2, Min_sum, Max_sum, Acc) ->
    Sum = digit_sum(N),
    if
        Min_sum =< Sum, Sum =< Max_sum ->
            count_good_ints(N + 1, N2, Min_sum, Max_sum, Acc + 1);
        true ->
            count_good_ints(N + 1, N2, Min_sum, Max_sum, Acc)
    end rem 1000000007.

digit_sum(0) -> 0;
digit_sum(X) -> X rem 10 + digit_sum(X div 10).
